data.description: CORNER LOT. Sturdy brick BASEMENT RANCH style home nestled on a beautiful OVERSIZED lot. Detached Garage with concrete floor & a fenced back yard. Beautiful Country Style Kitchen with a cozy Dining area. The large yard boasts apple and pear trees, muscadine grape vines and blackberry bushes. There are 3 bedrooms on the main level with one full bathroom. You can gain access to the FINISHED OFF lower level from inside the home or thru the LOWER LEVEL walkout door. On the Lower Level you have a 4th bedroom, full bathroom, plus a LARGE seating area as well as a Washer/Dryer area.   Electric log fireplace BOX does not convey.
